high_descs: cross the kitchen to the counter between the fridge and stove
pick up the apple sitting on the knife
take the apple and cross the kitchen to the microwave and open it
place the apple inside and turn it on and then take out the apple
go to the fridge and open it
place the apple inside the fridge on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Warm up the apple and put it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter that's to the left of the stove in front of you to  your left.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you to the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink that's in front of you to your left.
Cook the apple in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge that's in front of you to your left.
Put the apple on the middle shelf of the fridge then close the door..
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the counter on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Turn right to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the apple in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an apple to put it in the fridge.
